    <field_description order="before">
      <para>Data cache clean requirements for instruction to data coherence. The meaning of this bit is:</para>
    </field_description>
    <field_values>
      <field_value_instance>
        <field_value>0b0</field_value>
        <field_value_description>
          <para>Data cache clean to the Point of Unification is required for instruction to data coherence, unless CLIDR.LoC == <binarynumber>0b000</binarynumber> or (CLIDR.LoUIS == <binarynumber>0b000</binarynumber> &amp;&amp; CLIDR.LoUU == <binarynumber>0b000</binarynumber>).</para>
