<para>The value <binarynumber>0b00</binarynumber> is permitted only in an implementation that includes <xref browsertext="FEAT_VPIPT" filename="A_armv8_architecture_extensions.fm" linkend="v8.2.PIPTV"/>.</para></field_description>
